Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:14.35,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}tsumetai ameagari no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.48,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}kawaita kuuki furete mitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:27.07,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}mebaeru hana no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:33.33,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}omoi no kakera afurete kuru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:46.01,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}kono te ni moraeta kimi no nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:55.01,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}takaramono ni naru mirai he michibiite kureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:23:04.94,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}zutto kimi no koe wo oikaketeita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:10.45,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}itsu kara nan darou tsuyoku natta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:17.54,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}kiiroi sekai sagashita mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:25.25,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}tabiji no hate ni kitto mitsukaru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:14.35,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}Po mrazivé vichřici,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.48,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}v níž suchý vítr vál,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:27.07,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}se ve mně začínají vytvářet různé pocity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:33.33,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}jako v květině, která brzy vykvete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:46.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}Ve svých rukou stále cítím tvé teplo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:55.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}které mě vede k budoucnosti, jíž si mohu vážit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:23:04.94,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}Stále jdu za tvým hlasem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:10.45,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}a náhle jsme spolu zesílili.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:17.54,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}Na konci své cesty jistě najdeme,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:25.25,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur8}co hledali jsme v tomto světě.
